**New Makeup Batch Starting 16th June!**

We’re excited to start our new makeup course on **16th June**! In this 30-day course, you’ll learn **7 stunning makeup looks** including **Haldi, Mehendi, Bridal, Sangeet, Cocktail, Dark Skin, and Mature Skin** – plus **airbrush techniques**!

We provide only **top-quality international products** like Estee Lauder, Forever52, Huda Beauty, and more for practice. All products are **given by the academy** so you can focus on learning.

Our expert stylists from Delhi will train you with the **latest and most advanced techniques** in the market. You'll also get **2 professional portfolios** and **10 business sessions** to grow your career and your social media presence – something no other academy is offering!

We’ve already trained over **8,000 happy students**, and we’re proud to give each one personal attention and care. Your career and dreams matter to us!
